## 🗂️ Folder Structure
   
Here’s a quick reference to understand the folder layout:

Cinephile-Corner/
│
├── assets/
│   ├── css/                # CSS files (e.g., homepage.css, index.css)
│   ├── js/                 # JavaScript files (e.g., homepage.js)
│   ├── images/             # All images (posters, banners)
│   └── videos/             # Movie trailers and clips
│
├── fontawesome/            # Font Awesome resources (icons, fonts)
├── pages/                  # HTML files (e.g., index.html, subscription.html)
├── README.md               # Project Overview (this file)
└── .gitignore              # Files to be ignored by Git

